{"tid":1164312,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"葉問4劇情","createTime":"2019-05-21T03:43:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-21T05:04:03.000Z","uid":52215,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6329655a4f57be83f71210fa6091a4b3abd8020c","tid":1164312,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T03:43:14.000Z","msg":"葉問（甄子丹飾）在妻子過世後，與兒子過著簡單生活，他的徒弟李小龍（陳國坤飾）遠赴美國，在美國開武術館教授外國人武術，因得罪了當地唐人街的其他武館，處處受到當地人刁難。隨後葉問前往美國到徒弟李小龍開的武術館，卻見到了華人慘遭白人歧視與欺壓，決定挑戰白人強武，並以詠春及德性服人，立於天地，讓世界看見，最後成為ㄧ代宗師。"},{"pid":"1e5bb5d2afd068d08cb5eb4af1889fa90603b6df","tid":1164312,"uid":17619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T03:45:18.000Z","msg":"大概估到5係點發展"},{"pid":"9af2220b55ceb3df0d5668c44139ef592a919613","tid":1164312,"uid":176368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T03:47:29.000Z","msg":"當武俠片睇好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfe71c9404dde3bb826219aa1cbac24c97f51fb1","tid":1164312,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e5bb5d2afd068d08cb5eb4af1889fa90603b6df","tid":1164312,"uid":17619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T03:45:18.000Z","msg":"大概估到5係點發展"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T03:48:54.000Z","msg":"打菲利"},{"pid":"e6a6e9c43dd43a2bdc46749ea6fb1450a16f586d","tid":1164312,"uid":19712,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T03:51:59.000Z","msg":"葉問5 打關公<br />\n葉問6 打外星人<br />\n葉問7 打外太空<br />\n葉問8 打其他次元<br />\n葉問9 打閻王<br />\n葉問之葉問重生"},{"pid":"c01a622cc6452728d5fe9ac3d82bd0e943e82d03","tid":1164312,"uid":157304,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T03:54:29.000Z","msg":"好撚心唔好成日拖李小龍落水啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人哋根本唔係用中國武術<br />\n一腳踢撚到班fing春傻仔死十次都仲得<br />\n使撚你葉問阿伯搭飛機去美國救咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />行路企穩未呀"},{"pid":"22